          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有这等事。凡成仙之人，神气充足，再不思睡。怎么这等困倦，莫不是被人暗"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "算了？取法水来，待我救醒他们便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众道士同下，同上，同递水。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "清风、明月醒来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清风、明月同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙师吓，唐三藏带来三个徒弟，就像强盗一般，十分凶狠，又将弟子行挫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他们怎生样凶狠？"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们请唐三藏奉过了茶，遵仙师法旨，就将人参果二枚奉敬。他见了，说是三"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝未满的婴孩，十分害怕，不敢吃。谁想那三个凶狠的徒弟，私自盗取人参果"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三枚吃了。我们知道后，与他讲论。谁想那泼猴发怒起来，把果树连根拔却，"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "连夜逃走了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好放肆的泼猴，辄敢如此猖狂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众道士",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启问仙师，那泼猴怎生凶顽？"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们不知。那孙悟空他是个太乙散仙。曾记大闹天宫，神通广大。但我这样人"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参果树，先天地而长，后日月而不老。那三千年一花、三千年一实的蟠桃，也"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "比不上他的灵道。如八千岁为春，八千岁为秋的大椿，也敌不过他的悠久。怎"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "料被一个小畜牲，轻轻儿倒拔了去。我怎肯轻饶恕。清风、明月，你二人在家"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "收拾刑具。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清风、明月同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们跟我前去，拿他们回来，方消此恨。就此前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众道士同允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凶猴放肆太无理，"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒂固根深他刨起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "栽培活树再饶伊。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "镇元子→众道士",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "众道士→镇元子",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "镇元子→明月",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "明月→镇元子",
          "turns": 2
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "内白": 1,
          "stage_direction": 8,
          "同白": 5,
          "白": 7,
