    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众道士",
        "唐僧",
        "孙悟空",
        "拔倒仙树连夜走",
        "明月",
        "清风",
        "猪悟能",
        "镇元子"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、猪悟能、沙悟净、唐僧同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是山僻旷野之处，何不下马，暂歇片时再行如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，你看后面旋风骤起，诚恐镇元子追来。且趱上前去，再作道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祸是你惹得，连累我们，一夜不曾歇脚，也不顾人死活。这等怕他，何苦又去"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拔坏他的果树。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都是你馋痨蠢货，吃人参果起的事端。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我叫你偷果，谁叫你拔坏他的树根。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休得多言。作速前去趱行。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众道士、镇元子同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长老住马。贫道特地赶来，有事要请教。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贫僧失敬了。未知有何见教？"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长老是哪里来的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贫僧是大唐差往西天取经的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长老东土来，可曾在荒山经过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝山是何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万寿山五庄观便是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不曾经过，我们是上路来的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我把你这泼猴，你瞒哄谁来。我好意留人参果二枚，敬你师父。你反在我观中"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "偷吃了仙果，拔倒仙树，连夜逃走。不要嘴强，赔还我的树来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不赔你，你便怎么样呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猴头吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你今横行乱胡为，"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我岂容你便回归。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "捉你师徒与我赔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拔倒仙树连夜走"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老道言来敢相欺，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怒恼性儿把棒提。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人参果物不见奇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空举棒欲打镇元子，镇元子展袖收唐僧，孙悟空大起打，猪悟能、沙悟净同陷地井，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（镇元子笑，众人同下。清风、明月同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做事莫奸狡，休把人欺藐。烦恼不寻人，人自寻烦恼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙猴儿这斯偷吃了人参果，推倒了仙树。俺仙师回来大怒，前去追拿他了。命"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等收拾刑具伺候。你看那边祥云缭绕，一定是仙师来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众道士、镇元子同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蝎口念阿弥，尘尾全收缚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙师回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刑具可曾备下？"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "备下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（镇元子作拂袖，唐僧、孙悟空、猪悟能、沙悟净同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孽深由自造，报复总凭人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐僧、孙悟空、猪悟能、沙悟净同跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徒弟们。快取皮鞭来，且将这些和尚痛打一顿，方消我胸中之气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众道士",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先打哪个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老天保佑，不要打我才好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先打唐三藏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了。你们不可乱打。偷果是我，吃果是我，拔倒果树也是我。怎么打起我师"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先打他个管教不严。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我师父佛昆尼留下的五戒，第二戒是不许偷盗。这如今我便恳直的承当，吾佛"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "门正果，从无李代桃僵。你这妖道胡为，却也欺善怕恶。好笑，好笑。你也害"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怕孙爷爷的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好可恶。你倒说我怕你，不敢打。即如此，先与我重打这猴儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有道理。不免将这鞭数，寄在石头上，看他怎生奈何我。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众道士同打。场上作山。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众道士",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀仙师。打了这猴儿三十下，他只当不知，阶下一块顽石，打得粉碎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有这等事。是了，他用了个寄棒的法儿。也罢，你是打不着的了。我如今偏要"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打你师父。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又差了。偷果一事我师父不知。这是猪八戒起的念头。即打过了我，就该打他"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都是猴儿作的事，与我无干的吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽是我师兄的罪，你作师弟的，该替打几下，若不打猪八戒，再打我罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这泼猴好生狡猾奸顽，却又推三阻四。与我再打这泼猴！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我寄在柳树上便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众道士同打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众道士",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀仙师：又打了三十下，他只当不知，柳树上有三十条鞭痕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这泼猴，起先寄在顽石，如今又寄在柳树。我想打他是不怕的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众人过来。快与我架上大锅，烧起滚油，把这猴头炸了，才出我胸中恶气。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众道士同抬锅。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我使个法儿，打破他的锅底，看他怎生炸我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我对你说，还是打罢。那滚油锅里一炸就枯了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这却饶你不得了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好了，猴儿也怕了，不要炸到我身上来便好吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我却不怕，不免隐过原身，将那石狮子借他一用。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空下，执狮上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众道士",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启仙师：锅漏油流，猴儿倒站在一旁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然好猴儿。我且唬他一唬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众徒弟且将唐三藏拿下油锅里去炸起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休要炸我师父。还等我下油锅何如。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你在我跟前，卖弄手段。敢是要想捣我的锅灶么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你遇我就倒灶了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也知道你的本事。只是你今番越理欺心，纵有腾挪，脱不得我的手。就同你"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到西天去见佛祖，少不得要赔还我人参果，还我活树来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你太也小气了。若要活树，有甚难处。早说这话，可不省这一番的事。你放了"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我师父，我还你一棵活树便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若医得活树，我就放你师徒们。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此不打紧，放了他们，管教你果树重活便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既如此，暂将他师徒三个权为当头，单放这猴头去寻活树之法。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，这场祸事已解释了。徒弟去寻活树之法，不出三日之内。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若是三日不回，就要念起那话儿了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "知道了。师父请放心，我去就来。不免到那南海求菩萨去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祸到头来不自由，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急往南海去哀求。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "包管救得我师徒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这猴头既去寻觅活树之法，徒弟们且将他们师徒安顿内房，等他救活人参果树，"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "释放便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小小猴头寻诡计，"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万般难逃我这里。"
        },
        {
          "character": "镇元子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谅尔没有什么便宜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（镇元子下。）"
        }
      ],
